snippet.title: Minotaur Maze VR Gameplay (No commentary, Oculus Rift Cv1 and Oculus Touch)
snippet.description:
Title: Minotaur's Maze VR (Virtual Reality)
Genre: Indie, RPG, Early Access
Developer: Sisyphus Games
Publisher: Sisyphus Games 
Release Date: 13 Apr, 2017
Minotaur Maze VR In Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/531080/
About Minotaur Maze VR:
Minotaur's Maze is a tactical tabletop dungeon crawler brought to life in VR. 
_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ 
Steam Group VR: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/WorldVR
Steam Group Terror Horrror games: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/Terror_Horror_Games
Steam Group Love indies Games: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/LoveIndiesGames
_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ 
This channel is all about gameplay walkthrough, playthrough, review, preview, first impressions, tutorial, let's play, and more! The entire channel focuses on all things about video games and gaming content related. 
Subscribe here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmk_1iK7Dxd2VmIo1DwN0cw
